Methodology
Data Collection: Gather a labeled dataset of text reviews or social media posts with annotated sentiment labels—positive, negative, and neutral.
Data Preprocessing: Clean the text by converting to lowercase, removing punctuation, stop words, and special characters. Tokenize the text into words or n-grams to capture context.
Feature Extraction: Use TF-IDF vectorization to convert the processed text data into numerical features that represent the significance of words in the documents.
